hopobject.body: I'm from England usmedsci.com The Department of Health and Mental Hygiene (DHMH) joins the National Suicide Prevention Lifeline in recognizing National Suicide Prevention Week, September 8th-14th. This year's campaign encourages people to reach out through their community circles on Face book, Twitter and other social media platforms to highlight prevention efforts and link to the National Suicide Prevention Lifeline at www.facebook.com/800273TALK .
